dc_title_s: Commercial Revitalization Areas: Anne Arundel County, Maryland
dc_description_s: Commercial Revitalization Area layer for Anne Arundel County, MD. Council Bill No. 10-17 established designated Commercial Revitalization Areas in the county where commercial and industrial properties that are revitalized may receive tax credits. These areas were defined by the Office of Planning and Zoning.
dc_creator_sm: Anne Arundel County Office of Planning & Zoning; Research & GIS Division (Geographic Information Systems)
